text: Frankfort High School is the name of several high schools in the United States: *Frankfort High School (Michigan) - Frankfort, Michigan *Frankfort High School (Indiana) - Frankfort, Indiana *Frankfort High School (Kansas) - Frankfort, Kansas *Frankfort High School (Kentucky) - Frankfort, Kentucky *Frankfort High School (West Virginia) - Short Gap, West Virginia See also: *Frankford High School
